45","tid":764414,"uid":17008,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T05:10:23.000Z","msg":"D牌應該表裡各一個意思<br />\n<br />\n愚者逆位 就路飛佢地<br />\n法王逆位 就海多戰敗<br />\n援護 一係某人援助路飛 一係路飛援助某人"},{"pid":"dd8bdb2c5dafa28885259364b5c4fbe4d8a33f36","tid":764414,"uid":126736,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"da69405705f4cad7ec59739458ffa8ccc3f6ba05","tid":764414,"uid":52122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T04:25:20.000Z","msg":"其實有名刀係點<br />\n我意思係名刀既定位係點樣 <br />\n你武裝色夠勁乜野名刀都無用架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係佢好似錦衛門咁識出火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T05:12:11.000Z","msg":"好似囡囡啲名牌袋咁 <br />\n你用$10 袋又係裝野 <br />\n$30000 袋又係裝野<br />\n但自信+100 <br />\n<br />\n但最尾都係用黎裝野"},{"pid":"348c039cdd8ee0930513d2a6e8f21897624cbe84","tid":764414,"uid":147387,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T05:22:37.000Z","msg":"外行員錯了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6656efb8485e771c2981d570463735b0440f8638","tid":764414,"uid":140835,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T05:46:35.000Z","msg":"日文情報最尾咪講咗係邊個幫手"},{"pid":"7338b0ee50f0763dd742736b8c290b0cb6c793de","tid":764414,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1c03ce05fb42f482b84e55671f85d9ecb126d38","tid":764414,"uid":51670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f57c3a069d6743b0ede2a1346c59eeadb3c1c336","tid":764414,"uid":70968,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T03:34:45.000Z","msg":"又係時候估&ldquo;某人&rdquo;係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face